X.I t           no       Text t is italic. Quote to imbed blanks.
X.IP x          yes      Set prevailing indent to 5. Begin
X                        indented paragraph with hanging tag
X                        given by first argument.  Tag x is
X                        always placed on a separate line.
X.LP            yes      Same as .PP.
X.PP            yes      Begin paragraph.  Set prevailing
