X! .ds DA "\n(hh:\n(mm:\n(ss \n(mo/\n(dy/\n(yr"
X! .\"
X! .\" --------------------------------------------------------------------------
X! .\" main page heading
X! .\"
X! .\" fields are usually: 1-name, 2-section, 3-section name, 4-version, 5-date
X! .\" 1,2,3 are on header, 4,5 and page on footer. empty strings are skipped
X! .\" by making the arg "".
X! .\"
X! .de TH
X  .m1 1
X  .in 0
X! .po 0
X! .lt 65
X! .ll 65
X! .tl |$1 ($2)|$3|$1 ($2)|
X! .fo |$4|$5|%|
X  .in 5
X! .ll 65
X  ..
X! .\" --------------------------------------------------------------------------
X! .\" start relative indent (always 5 spaces...sorry)
X! .\"
X! .de RS
X! .sp
X! .in +5
X  ..
X! .\" --------------------------------------------------------------------------
X! .\" end relative indent
X! .\"
X! .de RE
X! .sp
X! .in -5
X  ..
X! .\" --------------------------------------------------------------------------
X! .\" indented paragraph with tag (from this line)
X! .\"
X! .de IP
X! .br
X! .sp 1
X! .in 5
X! \&$1 $2 $3 $4 $5 $6 $7 $8 $9
X! .br
X! .in +5
X  ..
X! .\" --------------------------------------------------------------------------
X! .\" start a new indented paragraph
X! .\"
X! .de pp
X! .sp 1
X! .in 5
X! .ti +5
X  ..
X! .\" --------------------------------------------------------------------------
X! .\" start a new unindented paragraph
X! .\"
X  .de PP
